com.millennialmedia.android
Class MMBroadcastReceiver

java.lang.Object
  android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      com.millennialmedia.android.MMBroadcastReceiver
Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public class MMBroadcastReceiver
extends BroadcastReceiver

A pre-made BroadcastReceiver to receiver MMAdViewSDK events. As a convenience the onReceive method implemented in this class will process Intents and call the appropriate functions you can override. Such as overlayOpened.
